OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening with some late
OL,7,Fbrightness. Then the rest of the night
OL,8,Fwill be dry with variable amounts of
OL,9,Fcloud.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA cloudy start in places.
OL,12,FOtherwise it will be dry with any
OL,13,Fcloud breaking up to leave a dry day
OL,14,Fwith some good spells of sunshine.
OL,15,FVery warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA dry
OL,18,Ffew days with long bright or sunny
OL,19,Fspells but the mornings starting a
OL,20,Flittle cloudy at times, particularly
OL,21,Faround the east coast. Very warm.
